<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7560> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7560" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "According to J. Suolahti, his rank in the consilium of P. Cornelius Lentulus Crus (218). Cos. 49, in Asia, as reported by Josephus (AJ 14.229, 238), was probably that of leg., lieut. or quaestor (Arctos 2, 1958, 152-163; cf. MRR 2.256).\n" .
